# Code ownership for claude-model-changer
#
# Every PR auto-requests review from the listed owners.
# Combined with branch protection's "Require review from Code Owners",
# this guarantees no PR can merge without R4CK's explicit approval.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <@owner> [<@owner> ...]
# More specific rules below override less specific ones above.

# Default: R4CK owns everything
*                       @R4CK

# Critical paths get an extra explicit mention (same owner today,
# but easy to add co-maintainers per area later):
.github/                @R4CK
scripts/analyze-complexity.js   @R4CK
scripts/lib/scoring.js          @R4CK
config/task-routing.json        @R4CK
hooks/hooks.json                @R4CK
.claude-plugin/                 @R4CK
